{"tid":1919240,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"南韓「KBS電視台員工」確診新冠肺炎","createTime":"2020-03-10T15:53:21.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-11T16:10:53.000Z","uid":74065,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"fd5293fc345d41da5bcd366a7990501e9187ecc1","tid":1919240,"uid":74065,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-10T15:53:21.000Z","msg":"快訊／南韓「KBS電視台員工」確診新冠肺炎 粉絲驚：Music Bank一堆愛豆去過了！<br />\n<br />\n南韓新冠肺炎（COVID-19）確診病例自2月下旬至今天天暴增，許多影視圈活動都受到影響<br />\n，不過疫情可能將面臨新一波衝擊。南韓三大電視台之一的KBS，10日晚間驚傳「員工確診<br />\n罹患新冠肺炎」，消息已獲得證實。<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/YUsUBG8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FYUsUBG8.jpg&h=2b568cce&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲南韓KBS電視台員工確診新冠肺炎。（圖／翻攝自官網）<br />\n<br />\n據韓媒綜合報導，KBS位於汝矣島的總部，一名內部人員確診罹患新冠肺炎，電視台已經證<br />\n實這項消息，並且在9日已經緊急隔離確診病患A先生和11位有密切互動的同事。同時緊急要<br />\n求其他工作人員，即日起在家遠距上班。<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/2M54y5t.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2F2M54y5t.jpg&h=78c7536b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲《Music Bank》是KPOP知名歌手宣傳期必去打歌的音樂節目。（圖／翻攝自官網）<br />\n<br />\n由於電視台出入許多藝人、演藝圈相關人員，消息一出也令粉絲們驚嚇的說：「天阿！他到<br />\n底接觸過誰？」更有粉絲無奈表示：「《Music Bank》都禁止粉絲去現場了，結果居然是內<br />\n部人員確診。」不過電視台也表示，該名員工工作時，都有配戴口罩和橡膠手套。"},{"pid":"1d389c29b248fbf7684041166f371823cf69341d","tid":1919240,"uid":46435,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-03-10T15:56:45.000Z","msg":"IZONE千祈唔好有事..😭"},{"pid":"16f54d54420ad91d267b46aa979141bf214a280a","tid":1919240,"uid":74065,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"1d389c29b248fbf7684041166f371823cf69341d","tid":1919240,"uid":46435,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-03-10T15:56:45.000Z","msg":"IZONE千祈唔好有事..😭"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-10T15:58:12.000Z","msg":"冇講明咩部門<br />\nIZONE冇得錄其他節目相對地都算安全啦😂"},{"pid":"52f0c1a8af38902d72febce1964ac728b177f69b","tid":1919240,"uid":89931,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-10T16:01:48.000Z","msg":"武漢肺炎* <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c821830cc22c31a3372224caf8c547c3191c7341","tid":1919240,"uid":255744,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-10T16:22:07.000Z","msg":"李屍2剛巧星期五開始播，警剔全球"},{"pid":"600d9a1059af202486f491649460381d8d6a7321","tid":1919240,"uid":229026,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1d389c29b248fbf7684041166f371823cf69341d","tid":1919240,"uid":46435,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-03-10T15:56:45.000Z","msg":"IZONE千祈唔好有事..😭"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-10T16:22:35.000Z","msg":"星期日末放了😢"},{"pid":"24c08bc0223e0468a888b8d5e4c04a653d12031d","tid":1919240,"uid":57868,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-10T16:24:59.000Z","msg":"之前音銀係咪有staff暗串恥笑izonecb即末放<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"974d73b123cdfe03630858af0550612cc0c8c567","tid":1919240,"uid":136738,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"16f54d54420ad91d267b46aa979141bf214a280a","tid":1919240,"uid":74065,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"1d389c29b248fbf7684041166f371823cf69341d","tid":1919240,"uid":46435,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-03-10T15:56:45.000Z","msg":"IZONE千祈唔好有事..😭"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-10T15:58:12.000Z","msg":"冇講明咩部門<br />\nIZONE冇得錄其他節目相對地都算安全啦😂"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-10T16:35:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8c080ad12c425ef9c81516b402acfa73ca3d3e2b","tid":1919240,"uid":256952,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-10T22:18:19.000Z","msg":"Itzy rip......"},{"pid":"944a4a9d4d79f431325614af292b5587c6650832","tid":1919240,"uid":228995,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-11T16:10:53.000Z","msg":"電視播雪花？"}]}